text: Hyla is a given name and surname. Notable people with the name Hyla include: *Hyla Bristow Stallard (1901–1973, known as H. B. Stallard), English runner and ophthalmologist *Hyla Willis, American artist *Adolf Hyła (1897–1965), Polish artist ==See also== *Hyla, a genus of tree frogs *Hylas (disambiguation)
